<D>__{n the side of a mountain rising up over britannia mine,}
<A>__{hudgens and fischer stand watching the activity below. jagged bolts of lightning and rumbling thunder echo around them. the sound of hissing comes up around them. suddenly, one by one, creatures start fading into visibility behind them. more and more creatures appear, fading visible, until there are dozens of xenomorph creatures stretching down the mountain side. hudgens looks back at his creature army. he lets an evil smile slip across his face. all at once, the creatures start leaping down the mountainside. as they run, they all start fading invisible.}
